      "bookSlug": "matthew",
      "chapterNumber": 19,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Matthew 19:2",
      "text": "ܘܐܬܘ ܒܬܪܗ ܟܢܫܐ ܤܓܝܐܐ ܘܐܤܝ ܐܢܘܢ ܬܡܢ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
